reates a pdf file with boxplots for all different features and labels\n\nParameters\n----------\nfeaturefile (str/dataframe):\n    Path to the featurefile/pandas dataframe\nlabels (dict):\n    Information about the contents of the well\ncolors (list):\n    List of colors to be used for the boxplots. Will use default colors if left empty\nshow_datapoints (bool):\n    Whether to show the individual datapoints on the boxplot\noutputpath (str):\n    Where to save the pdf-file. Required when passing a pandas dataframe.\ndiscern_wells (bool):\n    If True, will assign a random colour to datapoints from each well\nwell_amnt (int):\n    The amount of wells in the MEA-plate"]}, {"name": "CureQ._plotting.combined_feature_boxplots", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "folder", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "labels", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "colors", "type": null, "default": "..."}, {"name": "show_datapoints", "type": null, "default": "..."}, {"name": "discern_wells", "type": null, "default": "..."}, {"name": "well_amnt", "type": null, "default": "..."}], "returns": null, "documentation": ["Combine the features of multiple measurements together\n\nParameters\n----------\nfolder (str):\n    folder in which to look for featurefiles\nlabels (dict):\n    Information about the contents of the well\ncolors (list):\n    List of colors to be used for the boxplots. Will use default colors if left empty\nshow_datapoints (bool):\n    Whether to show the individual datapoints on the boxplot\ndiscern_wells (bool):\n    If True, will assign a random colour to datapoints from each well"]}, {"name": "CureQ._plotting.features_over_time", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "folder", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "labels", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "div_prefix", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "colors", "type": null, "default": "..."}, {"name": "show_datapoints", "type": null, "default": "..."}], "returns": null, "documentation": ["Show the different features between groups over time\n\nParameters\n----------\nfolder (str):\n    folder in which to look for featurefiles\nlabels (dict):\n    Information about the contents of the well\ndiv_prefix (str)\n    The prefix used to indicate the age of the cells (e.g. DIV, t)\ncolors (list):\n    List of colors to be used for the boxplots. Will use default colors if left empty\nshow_datapoints (bool):\n    Whether to show the individual datapoints on the boxplot"]}], "variables": [], "classes": [], "exports": []}, {"name": "CureQ._bandpass", "documentation": [], "functions": [{"name": "CureQ._bandpass.butter_bandpass", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "lowcut", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "highcut", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "fs", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "order", "type": null, "default": "..."}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "CureQ._bandpass.butter_bandpass_filter", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "data", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "parameters", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}], "variables": [], "classes": [], "exports": []}, {"name": "CureQ._features", "documentation": [], "functions": [{"name": "CureQ._features.electrode_features", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "well", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "parameters", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "CureQ._features.well_features", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "well", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "parameters", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "CureQ._features.feature_output", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "electrode_features", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "well_features", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "electrode_amnt", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documenta